(44599, 141259, 0, 1, 'Regret', 'Our very first single written by Kenneth and John. The 1st version was not suppose to be like this, it is much slower until KeN lost the entire session file and re-wrote it. The vocal was recorded in Kuching and it is produced and mix by KeN', '2011-03-03 00:00:00', 2010, 15, 0, 1, 'Mystical Mirage – Regrets\r\n\r\nVerse\r\nI close my eyes again, was it me who’s to be blame?\r\nI’m finding it hard to seek the truth\r\nIt was all just the same\r\nFading in time a year has gone now\r\nNothing seems to be the same again\r\nAll the moment of silence that reminds me\r\nHow’ve you got me running for the truth?\r\n\r\nIt was all confusing; I find it hard to say\r\n\r\nChorus\r\nI won’t want to see the end now,\r\nBut it’s all been thrown away,\r\nIt was all just too late now to say\r\nYou’ve regret\r\n\r\nVerse\r\nYou close your eyes and pray\r\nHope that everything’s undone,\r\nWish you could turn back time and see\r\nAll the blunders you’ve made\r\nFinding it hard to say you’re sorry\r\nNothing seems to be the same again\r\nI couldn’t believe everything you’ve said,\r\nPlease let it be alone\r\n\r\nIt was all confusing, you’ve find it hard to say\r\n\r\n\r\nChorus\r\nI won’t want to see the end now,\r\nBut it’s all been thrown away,\r\nIt was all just too late now to say\r\nYou’ve regret\r\n\r\nBridge\r\nNow that I’m gone, why is that all had to be this way?\r\nRemembering all the things you’ve said to me now, why’s that all a lie?\r\n\r\nChorus\r\nI won’t want to see the end now,\r\nBut it’s all been thrown away,\r\nIt was all just too late now to say\r\nYou’ve regret\r\n\r\n \r\n', '', 248, '', 'Kenneth and John', 'Kenneth', 'Kenneth', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-13 14:17:36', '2013-10-07 17:20:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44600, 141259, 0, 1, '什么时候', 'Ken wrote this song way back in time during 2007 for some artist, and now he re-wrote it into the rock version. Their 1st ever chinese song in their discography', '2012-03-13 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 1, '神秘幻影 – 什么时候\r\n\r\n\r\nVERSE\r\n什么时候我的心开始跳了 \r\n什么时候我的梦流连开了  \r\n丘比特是如何悄悄进来的 \r\n爱会不会再次受伤如刀割 \r\n什么时候我的天空多了色彩 \r\n什么时候头上的烟霾已不在 \r\n停止的心 该不该再活跃起来 \r\n过去曾经 是否有望再从来 \r\n\r\nCHORUS\r\n世界多了一个你  \r\n是不知 是不觉 \r\n一秒钟少看你  \r\n休而不息睡难眠   \r\n\r\n世界不再怕孤寂 \r\n分享快乐人难移 \r\n包袱搜索再背起 \r\n俩人一起扛到底  \r\n\r\nVERSE\r\n什么时候我的心开始跳了  \r\n什么时候我的梦流连开了  \r\n丘比特是如何悄悄进来的  \r\n爱会不会再次受伤如刀割  \r\n什么时候我的天空多了色彩  \r\n什么时候头上的烟霾已不在  \r\n停止的心 该不该再活跃起来  \r\n过去曾经 是否有望再从来  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCHORUS\r\n世界多了一个你  \r\n是不知 是不觉 \r\n一秒钟少看你 \r\n休而不息睡难眠 \r\n世界不再怕孤寂 \r\n分享快乐人难移 \r\n包袱搜索再背起 \r\n俩人一起扛到底  \r\nCHORUS\r\n世界多了一个你  \r\n是不知 是不觉 \r\n一秒钟少看你 \r\n休而不息睡难眠 \r\n\r\n世界不再怕孤寂 \r\n分享快乐人难移 \r\n包袱搜索再背起 \r\n俩人一起扛到底  \r\n', '', 232, '', 'Kenneth', 'Casper黃羽承', 'Kenneth', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-13 14:19:48', '2013-10-07 17:20:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44601, 141259, 0, 1, 'Don''t Stay', 'Our 3rd Single, Ken wrote this for his school project, then eventually he took to his discography. This song is played every saturday in Kuching sarawak , Hit.fm Kuching radio station. ', '2012-03-13 00:00:00', 2010, 0, 2, 1, 'Mystical Mirage – Don’t stay\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse\r\nWhat you waiting for, I’m here to stay for now\r\nThe wind kept still leaving all the mess behind\r\nLooks like its ok, but in my heart it hurt so bad\r\nAnd I felt unease now, waiting for an answer to this mess\r\nWhen the time has come to let go hopes and dreams I have for now\r\n\r\nChorus\r\nIt’s hard to say, when you’re down without a words to seek the truth\r\nI’m here to stay, but it’s been so long now, and I don’t want you to stay\r\n\r\nVerse\r\nIt’s been a while now, I’m letting go the pain I’ve barred\r\nI’ve never felt this way; I shouldn’t pin my hopes on you\r\nYou never cared for me; I’m hanging by myself alone\r\nAnd I felt distress now, waiting for an answer to break through\r\nOf all the things you’ve done, it’s time to pack and leave the door right now\r\n\r\nChorus\r\nIt’s hard to say, when you’re down without a words to seek the truth\r\nI’m here to stay, but it’s been so long now, and I don’t want you to stay\r\nSo stay away (Stay away, just stay away)\r\nIt’s hard to say, when you’re down without a words to make it through\r\nAnd I understand, that it’s been so long now, and I don’t want you to stay\r\nBridge\r\nSo let me know when you’re gone, \r\nIt’s O.K, to let go of everything you ever say\r\n\r\nChorus\r\nIt’s hard to say, when you’re down without a words to seek the truth\r\nI’m here to stay, but it’s been so long now, and I don’t want you to stay\r\nSo stay away (Stay away, just stay away)\r\nIt’s hard to say, when you’re down without a words to make it through\r\nAnd I understand, that it’s been so long now, and I don’t want you to stay\r\nSo stay away\r\n', '', 252, '', 'Kenneth ', 'Kenneth', 'Kenneth', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-13 14:22:16', '2013-10-07 17:20:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44602, 141259, 0, 1, 'You', 'This song is not properly recorded yet but it is finished, Ken just have to hit the studio to finish the vocal. It''s not fully release on the discography', '2012-03-13 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 2, 1, 'Mystical Mirage  - You\r\n\r\nVerse\r\nRunning away from all the things that thrilled me \r\nIt’s hard to forget that pain\r\nYou came along and sweep away those shattered broken heart\r\nI‘ve never felt this much joy, when I’m with you all this time\r\n\r\nPre-Chorus\r\nI’m never gonna leave you, fade away in time\r\nAll that I wish for is to tell you\r\nThe way that I feel \r\n\r\nChorus:\r\nYou, Promise me that you will never gonna let me torn in pieces \r\nThat will be the only thing that kept me trip and falling all the way\r\nYou, take the chance and lighten up the day so that my life wouldn’t be the same\r\nEverything you did has break the silence all this time\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse 2\r\nYou came into my life and I can see you filled my hollow heart\r\nMaking me think that it was worth it, everything was kept in place\r\nI hope it will last and there’s a choice,\r\nLet it go or let it stay\r\n\r\nPre-Chorus\r\nI’m never gonna leave you, fade away in time\r\nAll that I wish for is to tell you\r\nThe way that I feel \r\n\r\nChorus:\r\nYou, Promise me that you will never gonna let me torn in pieces \r\nThat will be the only thing that kept me trip and falling all the way\r\nYou, take the chance and lighten up the day so that my life wouldn’t be the same\r\nEverything you did has break the silence all this time\r\n', '', 292, '', 'Kenneth ', 'Kenneth', 'Kenneth', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-13 14:24:56', '2013-10-07 17:20:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
